This paper discusses a type system and data definition language for property graphs, which are commonly used in database management and artificial intelligence applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
